pdf\" target=\"_blank\">strategic plans</a> going out to 2029. This was done</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283601718/image_1283601718.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742160-is-at-and-t-becoming-a-growth-stock", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 01:31:52"}, {"id": "4742164", "title": "Super Micro Computer: That Was A Game Changer", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1935446586/image_1935446586.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"\u0420\u0443\u043a\u0430, \u0434\u0435\u0440\u0436\u0430\u0449\u0430\u044f \u0443\u0432\u0435\u043b\u0438\u0447\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044c\u043d\u043e\u0435 \u0441\u0442\u0435\u043a\u043b\u043e \u043d\u0430\u0434 \u0441\u0435\u0440\u0442\u0438\u0444\u0438\u043a\u0430\u0442\u043e\u043c \u043a\u0430\u0447\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0430.\" data-id=\"1935446586\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1935446586/image_1935446586.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1935446586/image_1935446586.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1935446586/image_1935446586.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1935446586/image_1935446586.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1935446586/image_1935446586.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1935446586/image_1935446586.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1935446586/image_1935446586.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1935446586/image_1935446586.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (